articles.author: Emma Agyemang
articles.title: Global minimum tax on multinationals goes live to raise up to $220bn - Financial Times
articles.description: After years of OECD talks, ‘critical mass’ of nations to apply at least 15% rate from January
articles.content: Big multinational companies will from Monday be subject to a global minimum tax for the first time, as landmark cross-border tax reforms go live, seeking to raise up to $220bn in extra annual revenue… [+4646 chars]
